The current code can also cause leaks because the code inside the following if-caluse will never be executed and hence your listener and updater will be there until the document is no longer referenced (e.g. by another editor).

        IDocument document = getDocument();
        if (document != null) {
            document.removeDocumentListener(documentListener);
            document.removePositionUpdater(positionUpdater);
        }
